milestones.description: Kevin O'Brien and Porterfield's 227-run partnership is IRE's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 88 between Kevin O'Brien and Porterfield
Porterfield has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for IRE breaking Jeremy Bray's record
Kevin O'Brien's 142 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IRE), surpassing Jeremy Bray's 116
Kevin O'Brien has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs for IRE, going past Johnston's 6
Andre Botha has become the top wicket-taker for IRE in ODIs with 11 wickets, going past Dave Langford-Smith's 9
Kevin O'Brien has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray's 4
Kevin O'Brien has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (76) in an innings in ODIs for IRE, going past Jeremy Bray's 64
Kevin O'Brien and Porterfield's 227-run partnership is IRE's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 88 between Porterfield and Kevin O'Brien
Andre Botha has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for IRE, going past Johnston
